    "description": "Grow your career with Malabar Gold & Diamonds Asia Pacific Associates! We are hiring a Floor Manager for our Chandigarh team. Be part of a workplace that celebrates innovation, diversity, and performance.\n\nAbout Malabar Gold & Diamonds Asia Pacific Associates:\nMalabar Gold & Diamonds Asia Pacific Associates is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Build relationships with regular customers to drive loyalty\n• Maintain high standards of store hygiene and cleanliness\n• Conduct regular stock audits and prevent pilferage\n• Manage shrinkage and reduce stock discrepancies\n• Assist in recruiting, onboarding, and performance management of staff\n• Implement promotional activities and in-store campaigns\n• Train and motivate the sales team to deliver excellent service\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Tech / B.E. in Computer Science or related discipline\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Team Leadership\n• Proficiency in Inventory Management\n• Proficiency in Retail Analytics\n• Proficiency in POS Systems\n• Proficiency in Category Management\n• Proficiency in SAP Retail\n• Proficiency in Sales Techniques\n• Proficiency in E-commerce Integration\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Chandigarh, Punjab, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Malabar Gold & Diamonds Asia Pacific Associates!",
